The Executive Vice Chairman, EVC, and Chief Executive Officer, CEO, of the Nigerian Communications Commission, NCC, Prof Umar Danbatta featured as a guest on AREWA24 TV during the maiden edition of the Telecom Television Dialogue. The event, held on May 29th, 2022, also featured the likes of the Director, Consumer Affairs (DCA), NCC, Efosa Idehen; and the Director Technical Standards and Network Integrity (DTSNI), NCC, Bako Wakil. VIDEO: 